size=1> In West Karana at the village nearest the Qeynos Hills zone, there is a Bard, Misty Storyswapper.  Misty ranges from lvl 13-17, always drops a mandolin (1pp+), the occasional word, rune, page and the occasional Raw-hide armor.  She is great exp.<br>
<br>
When you first get there con her.  If your faction is indiffernet, apprehansive or dubious, I would suggest going and doing the bard report quest in qeynos first.  Get you faction to warmly, abouit a dozen or so bard report runs.  Then come back here and kill Misty.  The bard reporst quest offsets the faction hits taken for killing her.<br>
<br>
I did level 15 about 4 hours and made over 50pp.   <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> Litherix</span><br> <span class=usertitle>Unregistered User</span><br>   <font color=#333333>(5/8/00 7:33:44 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm40.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=5.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   12-16</span><hr size=1> East karana has lots of stuff to kill in this level range.   Carrion spiders are<br>
