is close by for emergencies, and they drop silk that can fetch you some nice<br>
cash.   There are also snakes, lion mat/patriarchs, and wolves to fight.  and<br>
no faction issues.  the zone has merchants for buying food/arrows/bandages<br>
too. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#dcdeed><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> Satren</span><br> <span class=usertitle>Unregistered User</span><br>   <font color=#333333>(5/29/00 7:16:35 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm40.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=5.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   12-16</span><hr size=1> TWO WORDS WEST COMMONS <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> Breckin</span><br> <span class=usertitle>Unregistered User</span><br>   <font color=#333333>(6/5/00 2:20:20 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm40.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=5.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Two words for you</span><hr size=1> I am not sure what race you are but I bulit my mage to lvl 16 from lvl 11 in <br>
